modName: Outta this world babes Julia - DELETED
summary: This is a preset of my charcter in Skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
Succubus preset of my character in Skyrim.

To let her look like in the screenshot you have to use these mods: 

Succubus Race: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/22903/?
Race menu: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?
KS-Hair: http://robton.nu/kshairdos/
HN66s Long Eye Lashes: http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27783/?
CBBE (Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition): http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?


otherwise it could look a little deformed and misshapen^^

Installation:        - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/65861/?
          - extract zip file
          - default install-path should be - C:\Program Files (x86)\Steam\steamapps\common\The Elder Scrolls V                             Skyrim\Data\SKSE\Plugins\CharGen\Presets
            or something like that

This should be all for now...

Other Presets will follow ;)

Thanks to:       [b]humannature66[/b]
[b]Nikitaa[/b]
